Our AddressBook helps us save company details, so information on
companies are stored instead of a person.

This is done by refactoring instances of Person to Company.
Add several icon images

commitResults.messageTitle: Add change company status method in EditCommand
Expand find to include application and tags
commitResults.messageBody:
Searching by company name only will not yield many functional
results.

Expanding the find command to include words in application description
and tags can help users search for companies in the company list more effectively.

This is done by expanding the test method in NameContainsKeywordsPredicate to include
company application name, description and tags.

Without a logger, it may be difficult to track where errors occur and
document them properly to aid with debugging in the future.

Having a logger will help speed up the process of debugging.

specific company by index.
